reviews.review:
In this game:
- you will be killed constantly, if you do not have patience or a weak mind, then this game is not for you;
- campers make up 80% of all players;
- models merge with gray textures, it will be difficult to kill the camper;
- weapon recoil is slightly easier than in DOD:Source, but not much better;
- there are about 7 servers where more than 10-15 players are recruited;
- very few toxic players, usually all kind and cheerful;
- problems with hitboxes that meet with recoil and this becomes a sign of unplayability.

Despite the disadvantages, I still love this game because there are still adequate people and a very nice atmosphere.
